divs: sighting detailsnovember 14,2008, my son and i were hunting in corona, new mexico. we were hunting in state land where no one ever hunts the area. it happened about 6:30 am on the morning of our hunting day. we came along a nice big buck. i shot at it, but the buck kept going we didn't know for sure if we hit it . we were tracking the deer in bad terraine where i didn't think no one was ever in this mountain terraine . when we came up to this strange object i was driving the for wheeler, my son was on the back. i told my son," what is that ". i knew it was nothing fom this world, i told my son [cms\tg\pid]. that it is a ufo alien. it scared the holy cow out of us. we found the head under a pine tree, and there were bones scattered arond the area where i found the head. my family and i were from corona, nm. we moved from corona in 1968 to belen, nm. where my family and i live. my sister who is 60 years of age told me that a ufo crashed in corona, nm on the day of 1964 on a private ranch or state land. approximatly 80 miles from the town of roswell, nm crash site. i don't want to send a video clip or a photo at this time. sincerly, [cms\tg\pid]
